data.description: You have been looking? You just found it! 3 bedroom, 2 bath immaculate easy flow move in ready home.  Add your belongings and you will be easily settled into your new home!  Caledonia school district, easy access to Columbus Air Force Base. Large Master, Updated kitchen with stainless appliances, open living and dining area, very nice large laundry room. Roomy back patio overlooks a backyard ready for entertaining or just  sitting enjoyng a peaceful morning or evening. Amenities include tankless water heater, solar panel, stainless appliances. Don't miss taking a look at this one! 2024-01-24
